<plot>"Crossover" journeys around the planet to reveal how basketball is more than an American export; it belongs to the entire world. As a means of survival during war, of hope in the face of poverty, of cultural fusion happening everywhere, basketball is the miracle of the whole world playing together. Film production for "Crossover" extends across America to Eastern and Western Europe, Africa and Asia. The film blends spoken word poetry, world music and stunning imagery to reveal a unique perspective on how sports can unify humankind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?119542</url></doc>
